  function! s:OpenTTerminal()
    " Only remap `<Esc>` in this buffer so it doesn't interfere
    " with commands that spawn terminals like `fzf`
    tabnew
    terminal zsh
    tnoremap <buffer> <Esc> <C-\><C-n>
  endfunction
  function! s:OpenTerminal()
    " Only remap `<Esc>` in this buffer so it doesn't interfere
    " with commands that spawn terminals like `fzf`
    split
